Game information:

In the game The Walking Dead: Season 2 continues the story of Clementine,
a girl orphaned due to invasion of the living dead. Forced to take care
of herself, she learns to survive in a crazy world.

Many months have passed since the events of The Walking Dead: Season 1,
and Clementine is trying to secure safety. But how can survive normal
child, when the living is no better and sometimes worse than dead?
Playing as Clementine, you will encounter situations and dilemmas,
test your moral character and instinct of survival. In this sequel
to one of the best games of 2012 your decisions and actions change history
